DAPHNE: (IN ENGLISH)
She was definitely
more talkative by the pool.

50:13.844 --> 50:15.554
And at dinner,
she was actually kinda nice.

50:15.637 --> 50:19.057
Well... (SNIFFS)
...now that he's loaded,

50:19.141 --> 50:21.351
do you think
he regrets marrying such a dud?

50:21.435 --> 50:23.562
Cam, I wanna FaceTime
them again.

50:23.645 --> 50:25.105
-CAMERON: What? (CHUCKLES)
-Please?

50:25.188 --> 50:26.898
CAMERON: Honey, come on.
We just hung up.

50:26.982 --> 50:28.358
I know, but I miss Emma so much.

50:28.442 --> 50:29.568
CAMERON: I know.
Of course you do.

50:29.651 --> 50:30.861
But that's not the point,
all right?

50:30.944 --> 50:35.198
The point is... (SNIFFS)
...we're in Italy, honey. Okay?

50:35.282 --> 50:36.908
-DAPHNE: Mm-Hmm.
-We're on vacation.

50:36.992 --> 50:38.827
-Just you and me.
-DAPHNE: Yeah.

50:38.910 --> 50:42.080
-We need to enjoy it.
-(GASPS) Okay.

50:42.164 --> 50:43.832
-Just me and my baby.
-Ooh.

50:43.915 --> 50:46.334
-And you know what that means.
-What?

50:46.418 --> 50:48.670
-CAMERON: You need something.
-Mm-hmm.

50:48.754 --> 50:50.380
You need... (BREATHES DEEPLY)

50:50.464 --> 50:51.757
-...a tickle attack.
-No!

50:51.840 --> 50:53.967
-(CAMERON MUMBLING)
-(LAUGHS) No!

50:54.050 --> 50:55.719
-Please! Stop!
-Tickle, tickle, tickle.
I got you!

50:55.802 --> 50:58.346
(DAPHNE SCREAMING, LAUGHING)

50:58.430 --> 50:59.639
No, stop it!

50:59.723 --> 51:01.433
-(DAPHNE GRUNTING)
-CAMERON: (GRUNTS) Hey, hey!

51:01.516 --> 51:04.227
-Is he hurting her?
-(DAPHNE SCREAMING)

51:04.311 --> 51:07.522
-No! No... (GRUNTS)
-CAMERON: Hey! Tickle attack!

51:08.273 --> 51:10.233
(IMITATES MONKEY HOOTING)

51:10.317 --> 51:11.610
Monkey man, monkey man!

51:11.693 --> 51:12.778
(CHUCKLES) No.

51:12.861 --> 51:17.783
(DAPHNE AND CAMERON
CONTINUE SCREAMING AND LAUGHING)

51:20.160 --> 51:21.870
Thanks for making more
of an effort.

51:23.288 --> 51:25.582
I mean, yeah, they kind
of live in a bubble, but...

51:26.750 --> 51:28.293
they're fun, right?

51:29.377 --> 51:30.837
They don't vote, Ethan.

51:30.921 --> 51:35.217
I know. What the fuck?
They don't read the news.

51:35.300 --> 51:36.426
They don't read.

51:38.011 --> 51:40.138
It's like,
what do they even talk about?

51:40.222 --> 51:42.349
(INHALES) Is that what happens

51:42.432 --> 51:44.559
when you're rich for too long,
your brain just atrophies?

51:44.643 --> 51:47.979
(CHUCKLES)
I mean, they seem happy.

51:48.063 --> 51:51.650
No way. (SCOFFS) It's a front.

51:52.901 --> 51:57.739
It's good to have, you know,
diverse friends, I guess.

51:57.823 --> 52:01.493
(SCOFFS) Yeah, I think
we're their diverse friends.

52:01.576 --> 52:04.079
-(EXHALES)
-Their White-passing
diverse friends.

52:04.162 --> 52:05.872
Yeah, you're right. (SIGHS)

52:09.918 --> 52:11.378
♪ (PENSIVE MUSIC PLAYING) ♪

52:19.678 --> 52:21.721
(SIGHS)

52:25.892 --> 52:27.727
When we came up here
to get the suit,

52:28.603 --> 52:29.896
he just took all
of his clothes off

52:29.980 --> 52:32.732
in the middle of the room.
Like, naked.

52:34.693 --> 52:36.903
And then you--
Like, where were you?

52:36.987 --> 52:38.113
In the bathroom.

52:42.534 --> 52:43.785
Doesn't seem that weird.

52:46.246 --> 52:47.497
Just getting changed.

52:49.916 --> 52:54.045
(BREATHES DEEPLY, GRUNTS)

53:09.311 --> 53:11.104
♪ (MUSIC FADES) ♪

53:11.187 --> 53:12.230
(DAPHNE LAUGHING)

53:12.314 --> 53:14.065
CAMERON: Baby, come here!
Baby, come on.

53:14.149 --> 53:15.400
DAPHNE: No!

53:15.483 --> 53:20.280
♪ (OMINOUS MUSIC PLAYING) ♪

53:39.257 --> 53:40.175
(SCOFFS)

53:43.887 --> 53:45.931
♪ (MUSIC FADES) ♪

53:46.890 --> 53:50.143
♪ (TENSE MUSIC PLAYING) ♪

53:50.226 --> 53:51.353
(TANYA GASPS)

53:55.982 --> 53:57.025
Wow.

54:10.246 --> 54:12.248
(GREG WHISPERING INDISTINCTLY)

54:14.125 --> 54:15.126
All right, look.

54:15.210 --> 54:17.295
Look. Listen,
I don't wanna fucking talk

54:17.379 --> 54:19.255
about this right now, okay?

54:21.049 --> 54:25.345
Yes, I'm going to. Yeah.
This is not the time.

54:27.097 --> 54:28.139
Yes.

54:29.182 --> 54:30.892
-(KNOCKING ON DOOR)
-GREG: Fuck.

54:33.186 --> 54:35.563
-TANYA: Hi.
-(HESITATES) Hey.

54:35.647 --> 54:36.856
Who are you talking to?

54:36.940 --> 54:38.733
It's work. It's Bob.

54:38.817 --> 54:42.237
Oh, Bob. Well,
why were you whispering?

54:42.320 --> 54:44.990
I-- I thought you were trying
to get ready for bed.

54:45.073 --> 54:48.368
Oh, well. Guess what?

54:48.451 --> 54:50.495
-Huh?
-TANYA: Look what I found.

54:51.830 --> 54:55.625
-Oh, okay.
-Two macaroons!

54:55.709 --> 54:56.710
-GREG: Yeah, great.
-Yeah.

54:56.793 --> 54:58.294
I really did only eat three.

54:58.378 --> 54:59.879
Oh. Well, great.

54:59.963 --> 55:01.589
You had a whole
panna cotta at dinner.

55:03.633 --> 55:05.427
Well, eat them,
'cause you wanted 'em.

55:05.510 --> 55:06.636
I don't want them now.

55:06.720 --> 55:08.263
Why? Yeah, take them,
they're good.

55:08.346 --> 55:11.224
Tanya, I just brushed my teeth.
I'm on the phone.

55:14.811 --> 55:19.190
Uh, Bob, I gotta go...

55:19.274 --> 55:21.693
♪ (PENSIVE MUSIC PLAYING) ♪

55:41.212 --> 55:44.549
♪ (MUSIC TURNS DREAMY) ♪

55:50.180 --> 55:51.890
-DOMINIC: Here you go.
-Thank you.

55:51.973 --> 55:53.266
-DOMINIC: Cheers.
-Cheers.

55:54.267 --> 55:56.144
-(SLURPS)
-♪ (MUSIC FADES) ♪

55:58.021 --> 55:59.272
(DOMINIC GROANS)

56:07.405 --> 56:08.406
(CLICKS TONGUE, INHALES)

56:08.490 --> 56:10.909
I went down to the dock
when your boat arrived.

56:13.495 --> 56:15.288
I wanted to see
what you looked like.

56:16.915 --> 56:17.957
What'd you think?

56:20.543 --> 56:21.628
Very handsome.

56:25.673 --> 56:28.301
Thank you. (SLURPS)

56:28.384 --> 56:31.679
(INHALES)
And you're from Los Angeles.

56:31.763 --> 56:35.058
It's amazing. I always dreamt
of going to Los Angeles.

56:35.141 --> 56:36.267
It is my dream.

56:39.687 --> 56:42.065
Uh, I mean... (CHUCKLES)

56:44.275 --> 56:46.236
-(SLURPS)
-You should go.

56:50.115 --> 56:51.491
I don't have the money.

56:54.452 --> 56:57.413
(BREATHES DEEPLY)

56:57.914 --> 56:59.457
(SLURPS)

57:01.209 --> 57:02.335
(EXHALES)

57:07.382 --> 57:10.135
You seem like
a very nice person. Um...

57:12.262 --> 57:14.764
I'm just going through a lot
right now in my life.

57:14.848 --> 57:19.727
(INHALES)
So, it's-- it's, um...

57:19.811 --> 57:22.355
hard for me
to make conversation right now.

57:23.898 --> 57:27.986
(EXHALES) But you are very,
uh, beautiful.

57:33.449 --> 57:34.784
I'm glad you're here.

57:40.123 --> 57:42.709
(SLURPS, SMACKS LIPS)

57:42.792 --> 57:43.710
Allora...

57:43.793 --> 57:47.046
